    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good starting point. I'm looking to add some depth to the piece, though. Some people in the industry are saying these investigations are actually pretty dangerous because they could kill off the huge R&D budgets that drive innovation. How do you see that tension playing out—is it more about fixing a broken market or is there a real risk of the government overstepping and slowing down tech progress?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
